info.author: Eduardo Nogueira
info.description: The wagtail-autofixtures application can be used to automatically generate pages with aleatory content.The app main purpose is to load masses of randomly generated test data into your development database.This application its smart enough to choose between foreign keys and dynamic add inlines to the parent page.
